name: When you see life through the eyes of art

metadata.name: precious stone #1
metadata.description:
They talk about the beauty of the female, so it is said that this is a young twenties, like a rose, and this is a thirtieth shining as the sun, and this is a forty forty ripe, like a female fruit. Her beauty is not measured in years and years.
The female is like a plant, the more you water it with love and attention, the more its femininity and beauty increases, and the more creative it is in longing and giving.
